subtitleNullable: A dim sum food (Chinese snacks) image dataset with 50 categories
descriptionNullable:
# DimSum50 🔥

It is an image classification dataset about dim sum food, which are popular food among Chinese mainland and near nations and regions. The dataset has **50 categories** and **28,884 images** which divided into **training, validating, and testing subset in ratio of 8:1:1**.

You may feel free to check it on the [website](https://sites.google.com/view/dimsum50). All information about the paper and the dataset will be publish over it.
